				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpion451" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1918720); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1918720&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610163617" alt="Scorpion451" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1918720)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpion451" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1918720); return false;" >Scorpion451</a></span> <span class="odate time_1422893011 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">02 Feb 2015 16:03</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2223037">
									

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Ones&nbsp;that&nbsp;are&nbsp;permanently&nbsp;linked&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;black&nbsp;rabbit&nbsp;company&nbsp;for&nbsp;me:</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Most&nbsp;of&nbsp;these&nbsp;ran&nbsp;through&nbsp;my&nbsp;head&nbsp;at&nbsp;some&nbsp;point&nbsp;while&nbsp;reading&nbsp;this&nbsp;first&nbsp;arc.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>Glitch Mob's albums:
<ul>
<li>Animus Vox - &quot;Drive it like you stole it&quot; especially. &quot;Fortune Days&quot; is what was playing in my head after the last part of the epilogue where the credits would roll in a movie.</li>
<li>Love Death Immortality: &quot;Skullclub&quot; is my nomination for the Black Rabbit Company's themesong. &quot;I Need My Memory Back&quot; was Wizard in Phase 3, &quot;Can't Kill Us&quot;, &quot;Skytoucher&quot; and &quot;Carry the Sun&quot; were my mental background songs for most of Phase 4. (&quot;Carry the Sun&quot; starts at the line “Universal boundary passed. We have exited baseline.” 1:00 is “Then I’m with you.” 2:00 is &quot;100%&quot;. 3:10 is &quot;101%&quot;. 4:35 is &quot;Boss grinned at wizard, gave him a nod.&quot;)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Destroid - The Invasion : &quot;Bounce&quot; is 100% Nanami's concerto in Phase 4 (&quot;<em>It is too heavy!</em>&quot; X3). &quot;Flip the Switch&quot;, &quot;Activation&quot;, and &quot;Put It Down&quot; are best listened to as a set in that order, and make me think of their creation/early missions. Every song on this album is just begging to have a tale in this canon based off of it, really.</li>
<li>The Heavy - &quot;Short Change Hero&quot;</li>
<li>Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers - &quot;I won't back down&quot;</li>
<li>Zomboy - &quot;Pirate Hooker&quot;, &quot;Game Time&quot;, &quot;City 2 City&quot;, &quot;Raptor&quot;</li>
<li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J6-_qq9ySrc">Feint - &quot;Fury&quot;</a></li>
<li>Pegboard Nerds - Hero. The <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5lLclBfKj48">original mix</a> is epic, but the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FgFaSqrF_lw">Teminite Remix is an even better fit</a></li>
<li>Varien - <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_tIM1JK1YpM">&quot;Gunmetal Black&quot;</a></li>
<li>Anything by Nero</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

